\c 91 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 91\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Eegumsa Waaqayyoo Jala Jiraachuu
\m \bd 1\bd* Namni golgaa isa hundumaa gararraa jiru keessa jiraatu, gaaddisa isa hundumaa danda'uu jala in buufata;
\m \bd 2\bd* Waaqayyoon, "Ani sitti kooluu galeera, ati masaraa koo ti; ati Waaqayyo koo isa ani amanadhuu dha" in jedha.
\m \bd 3\bd* Waaqayyo, kiyyoo namni siif kaa'e, dha'icha nama balleessu irraas si oolcha;
\m \bd 4\bd* harka isaatiin si golbooba, bobaa isaa jalatti kooluu in galta, amanamummaan isaa gaachanaa fi marsaa siif in ta'a.
\m \bd 5\bd* Wanti halkan nama sodaachisu, xiyyi guyyaa namatti gad dhiifamus si hin sodaachisin!
\m \bd 6\bd* Dha'icha dukkanaan namatti dhufu, dhukkuba adeemaa saafaa nama balleessus hin sodaatin!
\m \bd 7\bd* Kumni tokko si bukkeetti kumni kudhanis gara mirga keetti yoo kufan iyyuu, wanti namatti dhufu kun sitti hin dhi'aatu.
\m \bd 8\bd* ati garuu ija keetiin ilaalte, gatii warra jal'ootaaf baafamu in argita.
\m \bd 9\bd* Ati, "Yaa Waaqayyo, ati isa ani kooluu itti galuu dha" jetteetta; isa hundumaa gararraa jirus iddoo kooluu itti galtu godhatteetta.
\m \bd 10\bd* Wanti hamaan sitti hin bu'u, dha'ichis mana keetti hin dhi'aatu.
\m \bd 11\bd* Karaa ati adeemtu hundumaatti, akka si eeganiif ergamoota isaa siif in abbooma.
\m \bd 12\bd* miilli kee dhagaatti akka hin buuneef, isaan harka irratti si baatu.
\m \bd 13\bd* Ati leencaa fi mar'ataa irra in ejjetta, leenca saafelaa fi jawwee in dhidhiitta.
\m \bd 14\bd* Waaqayyo immoo, "Sababii inni na jaallatee anatti maxxanuuf, ani isa nan oolcha; waan inni maqaa koo beekuufis, eegumsaan ol isa nan qaba.
\m \bd 15\bd* Inni ana in waammata, anis deebii nan kennaaf, yeroo rakkinaatti isaa wajjin nan jiraadha, achi keessaa isa nan baasa, ulfina akka inni argatus nan godha.
\m \bd 16\bd* Bara dheeraadhaan isa nan quufsa, akka ani fayyisus isa nan argisiisa" in jedha.
\b 
